## Test Structure

### Directory Layout

```
test/
├── application_system_test_case.rb  # System test base
├── test_helper.rb                   # Test configuration
├── controllers/                     # Controller tests
│   └── articles_controller_test.rb
├── models/                          # Model tests
│   ├── article_test.rb
│   └── user_test.rb
├── system/                          # System tests
│   ├── articles_test.rb
│   └── sessions_test.rb
├── jobs/                            # Job tests
│   └── article_notification_job_test.rb
├── mailers/                         # Mailer tests
│   └── article_mailer_test.rb
├── helpers/                         # Helper tests
│   └── articles_helper_test.rb
└── fixtures/                        # Test data
    ├── articles.yml
    └── users.yml
```

